  "descriptionKo": "OSDI은 시스템 분야(Operating Systems)의 주요 국제 학회입니다. 최근 acceptance rate는 15.9% (2024년, 50/315편)입니다. 주요 연구 키워드: Efficient, Distributed, Latency, Large Language Model, Language Model. 매년 7월 개최. CCF A등급, CORE A*, BK21 4점.",
  "descriptionEn": "OSDI is a leading international conference in Systems (Operating Systems). Recent acceptance rate: 15.9% (2024, 50/315 papers). Top research topics: Efficient, Distributed, Latency, Large Language Model, Language Model. Typically held in July. CCF rank A, CORE A*."
